Nigerian guys are very hard working but at the same damn they are extremely generous. For the rest of the world it might seem quite strange or somehow strange but in reality this is clever guys who have smart ways of making money and this is one of them. They give a ride to the girls and they get some rides themselves by giving rides to the girls. It is a win-win situation. My aunt’s colleague actually did the same when she visited Nigeria. She said it was great.

It is getting really hot and some of the Nigerians are swimming in the pool. Others are using the BBQ. At least some of them are enjoying their vacation in the sun. I did not see anyone skating which would be a good idea in my opinion.

Do not you possibly remember the Nigerian National Anthem from your school? his might sound weird but there are not a lot of people who actually know the words of it:

Actually celebrates the day in a prayer service and in some churches they celebrate for days. NIGERIANS ARE SOME WHAT RELIGIOUS PEOPLE.

All these games and outdoor activities happen actually all over Nigeria and everywhere people are having fun it is kinda common.
